<h2><span style="font-weight: 400;">2.Algorithms:</span></h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">For learring algorithm,following </span><a href="https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/0B04aUZ_O_zLWUG9abUpGX3lvMUU"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Competitive Programming 3 by Steven Halim</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;"> A to Z &nbsp;is the best approach.Also,</span><a href="https://www.rokomari.com/book/117663/%E0%A6%AA%E0%A7%8D%E0%A6%B0%E0%A7%8B%E0%A6%97%E0%A7%8D%E0%A6%B0%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%AE%E0%A6%BF%E0%A6%82-%E0%A6%95%E0%A6%A8%E0%A6%9F%E0%A7%87%E0%A6%B8%E0%A7%8D%E0%A6%9F-%E0%A6%A1%E0%A7%87%E0%A6%9F%E0%A6%BE-%E0%A6%B8%E0%A7%8D%E0%A6%9F%E0%A7%8D%E0%A6%B0%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%95%E0%A6%9A%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%B0-%E0%A6%93-%E0%A6%85%E0%A7%8D%E0%A6%AF%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%B2%E0%A6%97%E0%A6%B0%E0%A6%BF%E0%A6%A6%E0%A6%AE-(%E0%A6%B0%E0%A6%95%E0%A6%AE%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%B0%E0%A6%BF-%E0%A6%AC%E0%A7%87%E0%A6%B8%E0%A7%8D%E0%A6%9F%E0%A6%B8%E0%A7%87%E0%A6%B2%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%B0-%E0%A7%A7%E0%A7%A6)?ref=pbbr_t0_pg0_p7_pb3594"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Dawn of Programming Contest</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;"> covers about all the topics.But it is a bit difficult for beginners.</span></p>
