<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">All the sources mentioned above are very good.If you want to follow,then select one of them and learn everything from that source sequentially.Then you won&rsquo;t need to follow my syllabus.Don&rsquo;t learn one thing from one source and another thing from any other source randomly.This will decrease your progress of learning.</span></p>
